d period\", \"from\": 1979, \"to\": 1996}, {\"ngram\": \"a basket\", \"from\": 2004, \"to\": 2012}, {\"ngram\": \"Valeriane Ayayi\", \"from\": 2018, \"to\": 2033}, {\"ngram\": \"the game\", \"from\": 2039, \"to\": 2047}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Marine Fauthoux drained a three from near midcourt with the shot clock expiring to send the Bercy Arena crowd wild, but Napheesa Collier's putback ensured the teams headed into the break level at 25-25.\", \"from\": 2059, \"to\": 2261, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2059, \"end\": 2074, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marine_Fauthoux\", \"score\": 0.99989788370849, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Marine Fauthoux\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marine_Fauthoux\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marine_Fauthoux\"}, {\"begin\": 2151, \"end\": 2162, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Accor_Arena\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bercy Arena\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Accor_Arena\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Accor_Arena\"}, {\"begin\": 2179, \"end\": 2195, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Napheesa_Collier\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Napheesa Collier\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Napheesa_Collier\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Napheesa_Collier\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"midcourt\", \"from\": 2101, \"to\": 2109}, {\"ngram\": \"the shot clock\", \"from\": 2115, \"to\": 2129}, {\"ngram\": \"crowd\", \"from\": 2163, \"to\": 2168}, {\"ngram\": \"the teams\", \"from\": 2214, \"to\": 2223}, {\"ngram\": \"the break level\", \"from\": 2236, \"to\": 2251}]}, {\"sentence\": \"France strung together a 10-point run to start the third period as Fauthoux and Ayayi both nailed threes.\", \"from\": 2263, \"to\": 2368, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2263, \"